{{死刑}}

'''[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]'''在[[瓦哈比派|瓦哈比派]][[伊斯蘭教法|伊斯蘭教法]]的規範下，擁有嚴格的'''[[死刑|死刑]]制度'''，執行數量位居世界前列。根据[[人权观察|人权观察]]组织统计，2015年执行次数高达158<ref>{{cite web|title= Saudi Arabia ends 2015 with one final execution|url= https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-ends-2015-with-one-final-execution-a6793506.html|publisher= The Independent|accessdate= October 20, 2017|archive-date= 2018-12-08|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181208094947/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-ends-2015-with-one-final-execution-a6793506.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>，根据[[国际特赦组织|国际特赦组织]]统计，2016年则为至少154次<ref>{{cite web|title= Death sentences and executions in 2016|url= https://www.amnesty.org/en/documents/act50/5740/2017/en/|publisher= amnesty.org|accessdate= August 21, 2017|archive-date= 2017-10-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171011071624/https://www.amnesty.org/en/documents/act50/5740/2017/en/|dead-url= no}}</ref>，2017年为146次<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2018/04/death-penalty-facts-and-figures-2017/|title=The Death Penalty in 2017: Facts and Figures|publisher=[[Amnesty_International|Amnesty International]]|date=2018-04-12|accessdate=2018-07-16|archive-date=2019-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419061527/https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2018/04/death-penalty-facts-and-figures-2017/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

行刑時採取公開的方式，最常見办法是将受刑人用劍[[斬首|斬首]]<ref name= BBCexecutioner>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/2966790.stm |title=Saudi executioner tells all |date=5 June 2003 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=11 July 2011 |archive-date=2009-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090401233508/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/2966790.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[石刑|用乱石投击至死]]<ref name= FRD306>{{cite book |title=Saudi Arabia A Country Study |last=Federal Research Division |year=2004 |isbn=9781419146213 |page=304}}</ref>，其次是把受刑人釘死於[[十字架|十字架]]上<ref name= Miethe>{{cite book |title=Punishment: a comparative historical perspective |last=Miethe |first=Terance D. |coauthors=Lu, Hong |year=2004 |isbn=9780521605168 |page=63}}</ref>。

2007年至2010年間，共有345起執行公開處決的報告<ref name= Punishment>U.S. State Department Annual Human Rights Reports for Saudi Arabia 2007-2010: {{cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2010/nea/154472.htm |title=2010 Human Rights Report: Saudi Arabia |date=8 April 2011 |publisher=U.S. State Department |accessdate=11 July 2011 |archive-date=2012-05-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67yuCTsJx?url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/hrrpt/2010/nea/154472.htm |dead-url=no }}; {{cite web |url = http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2009/nea/136079.htm |title = 2009 Human Rights Report: Saudi Arabia |date = 11 March 2010 |publisher = U.S. State Department |accessdate = 11 July 2011 |archive-date = 2012-01-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120119202805/http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2009/nea/136079.htm |dead-url = no }}; {{cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2008/nea/119126.htm |title=2008 Human Rights Report: Saudi Arabia |date=25 February 2009 |publisher=U.S. State Department |accessdate=11 July 2011 |archive-date=2011-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110528211413/http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2008/nea/119126.htm |dead-url=no }}; {{cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2007/100605.htm |title=2007 Human Rights Report: Saudi Arabia |date=11 March 2008 |publisher=U.S. State Department |accessdate=11 July 2011 |archive-date=2011-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028004649/http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2007/100605.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最近一起因巫術而死刑定罪并成功執行的案例在2011年<ref name="witchcraft" />。2007年至2010年間沒有石刑的報告<ref>{{cite book |title=Islamic law and legal system: studies of Saudi Arabia |url=https://archive.org/details/islamiclawlegals00voge |last=Vogel |first=Frank E. |year=1999 |isbn=9789004110625 |page=[https://archive.org/details/islamiclawlegals00voge/page/246 246]}}</ref>，但1981至1992年間共有4起執行石刑報告<ref name= Punishment/>。

2020年4月，在沙烏地阿拉伯王儲[[穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼|穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼]]推動下，沙烏地阿拉伯政府宣布取消對未成年者實施死刑<ref>{{cite news |title=沙特阿拉伯取消未成年罪犯執行死刑 |url=https://www.singtao.ca/4224508/2020-04-27/news-%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E7%BD%AA%E7%8A%AF%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%AD%BB%E5%88%91/?variant=zh-hk |accessdate=2020-04-29 |archive-date=2020-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428041714/https://www.singtao.ca/4224508/2020-04-27/news-%e6%b2%99%e7%89%b9%e9%98%bf%e6%8b%89%e4%bc%af%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88%e6%9c%aa%e6%88%90%e5%b9%b4%e7%bd%aa%e7%8a%af%e5%9f%b7%e8%a1%8c%e6%ad%bb%e5%88%91/?variant=zh-hk |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

