== 爭議 ==
公開斬首及石刑已經在國際間引發不少批評的輿論<ref name= "Sharia Inc175">{{cite book |title=Sharia Incorporated: A Comparative Overview of the Legal Systems of Twelve Muslim Countries in Past and Present |url=https://archive.org/details/shariaincorporat00otto |last=Otto |first=Jan Michiel |coauthors= |year=2010 |isbn=978-90-8728-057-4 |page=[https://archive.org/details/shariaincorporat00otto/page/175 175]}}</ref>。外國籍勞工遭到處決的事件也引發批評，其中2011年9月一名來自[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]的民工因為「施行巫術」的罪名而被斬首<ref name="witchcraft">{{cite news |title=Sudanese man executed in Saudi Arabia for ’witchcraft and sorcery’ |url=http://www.sudantribune.com/spip.php?article40213 |newspaper=[[Sudan_Tribune|Sudan Tribune]] |date=24 September 2011 |accessdate=15 January 2013 |archive-date=2019-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613140303/http://www.sudantribune.com/spip.php?article40213 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]對此以「慘不忍睹」表達譴責<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/news-and-updates/saudi-arabia-executes-man-convicted-sorcery-2011-09-20 |title=Saudi Arabia executes man convicted of "sorcery" |author= |date=20 September 2011 |work= |publisher=[[Amnesty_International|Amnesty International]] |accessdate=15 January 2012 |archive-date=2013-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231070908/http://www.amnesty.org/en/news-and-updates/saudi-arabia-executes-man-convicted-sorcery-2011-09-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年1月，一名來自[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]的女傭[[Rizana_Nafeek|Rizana Nafeek]]因為照顧雇主的小孩不慎而使小孩窒息身亡，被法院判處斬首<ref name="the guardian1">{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/jan/13/saudi-arabia-treatment-foreign-workers |date=13 January 2013 |title=Saudi Arabia's treatment of foreign workers under fire after beheading of Sri Lankan maid |last=Chamberlain |first=Gethin |work=The Guardian |accessdate=14 January 2013 |archive-date=2013-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130705101001/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/jan/13/saudi-arabia-treatment-foreign-workers |dead-url=no }}</ref>，斯里蘭卡也因此召回大使<ref name="al jazeera1">{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/programmes/insidestory/2013/01/201311116530348352.html|date=12 January 2013|title=The plight of migrant workers in Saudi Arabia|work=Al Jazeera|accessdate=14 January 2013|archive-date=2018-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107123630/https://www.aljazeera.com/programmes/insidestory/2013/01/201311116530348352.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2013年，該國共有79名人犯被處決，其中外國人將近一半<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2010/nea/154472.htm |title=2010 Human Rights Report: Saudi Arabia |date=8 April 2011 |publisher=U.S. State Department |accessdate=11 July 2011 |archive-date=2012-05-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67yuCTsJx?url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/hrrpt/2010/nea/154472.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據國際特赦組織的統計，2010年至少​​有27位外籍劳工被處決，且截至2013年1月共超過45個外籍女傭在死囚牢房等待處決執行<ref>{{cite news |title=The beheading of a housemaid in Saudi Arabia highlights slave-like conditions |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/voices/comment/the-beheading-of-a-housemaid-in-saudi-arabia-highlights-slavelike-conditions-8451951.html |newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |date=15 January 2013 |accessdate=15 January 2013 |archive-date=2015-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926001756/http://www.independent.co.uk/voices/comment/the-beheading-of-a-housemaid-in-saudi-arabia-highlights-slavelike-conditions-8451951.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

